                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240916-94-off508 t18240916-94-cd509"></join>, a pair of trowsers, value 2 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18240916-94-victim823" type="victimName">
                           Francisco 
